    .main-content
      h1 Code of Conduct
      p We aim to create an inclusive and respectful community. By participating in this project, you agree to:

      ol
        li Be Respectful and Kind – No discrimination, harassment, or hate speech.
        li Share Appropriate Content – No offensive or plagiarized materials.
        li Engage Positively – Constructive discussions are encouraged.
        li Ensure Privacy and Safety – No sharing of private or personal information.

      h2 Ethical Considerations
      p The following points guide our ethical approach:

      ol
        li Data Privacy – Protect user data with secure authentication.
        li Content Moderation – Implement a system to report and review inappropriate content.
        li Inclusivity & Accessibility – Ensure usability for diverse dietary needs and users with disabilities.
        li Cultural Sensitivities – Respect religious and cultural significance in recipes.
        li Sustainability – Promote awareness and real solutions for reducing food waste.

